title: Pet Racer (2003)
description:
Great for kids and even some adults.

Game information : Release 2003
==================

The race is on, and it's going to be a fight to the finish. Pet Racer lets you play as your favorite four legged friends, giraffe, chicken, frog and more, racing your kart for first place in the Ultimate Animal Race Competition. Funny, colorful characters, 30 different settings, a variety of game modes and tons of fun power-ups like tomato launcher and wasp hive make Pet Racer a hit right to the finish line.

Installation Information :
==========================

Just mount or burn, then install the game and enjoy !
